<p>

<hr>

Some trips outside the White Mountains:
<ol>
  <li> In July 1997, I went on a
       <a href="../trips/tanzania/">safari in Tanzania</a>
  <li> In December 1998 I did some skiing  in
       <a href="switzerland">Switzerland</a> with Alex DeSherbinin.
  <li> In June 2000 my wife and I did some nice hikes in
       <a href="../trips/Madeira/">Madeira</a>.
  <li> In October 2001 I did a nice 
       <a href="SOSP01hike/">hike</a> at Lake Louise
       in Banff National Park while at SOSP.
  <li> In 2004 I visited and hiked in
       <a href="../trips/2004CostaRica">Costa Rica</a> 
  <li> In 2005 I hiked 
       <a href="../trips/2005ItalyRivaHike">near Riva del Garda</a> in Italy
  <li> In October 2007 I did a short walk at
       <a href="../trips/2007Oregon">Multnomah falls</a> in
       Columbia River Gorge.
</ol>


